<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Build an Event Flyer Page</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>

<body>
  <header class="header">
    <img class="pic" src="https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/labs/event.jpg" alt="Some colorful bunting hanging in sections">
    <h1>Annual Buntin' Championships</h1>
    <p class="p-head"><em>Get the buntin'</em> oot! It's time for the 3rd rendition of our annual Buntin' championships.</p>
    <p class="time-date"><strong>When:</strong> Probably never <strong>Where:</strong>In your imagination</p>
  </header>
  <hr>
  <main class="tab-box">
    <section class="event-tab">
      <h2>Featured Events</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><Strong>Longest Buntin'</strong><p class="event-item"> Who' Buntin' is longest? (Event record: 600 miles)</p></li>
        <li><strong>Buntin' Hunt</strong><p class="event-item">Rival teams try to locate the beggining of you Buntin' trail, first to locate the rivals buntin wins</p></li>
        <li><strong>Best Buntin'</strong><p class="event-item">Everyone will be hanging their Buntin' on our prestigious best overall Buntin' category</p></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section class="event-tab-2"> 
      <h2>Entertainment</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Buntin' Builder</strong><p class="event-item-2">Make your own Buntin' under the guidance of former world Buntin' champions</p></li>
        <li><strong>Buntin' Bunjee</strong><p class="event-item-2" id="event-item-2">Ever wondered if you can bunjee with Buntin'? Let's try! Will it work.. who knows?</p></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section class="event-tab-3">
      <h2>Food</h2>
      <ul>
        <li class="event-item-3"><strong>Buntin'</strong></li>
      </ul>
      <img class="pic-2" src="https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/labs/event.jpg" alt="more bunting">
    </section>
  </main>
  <hr>
  <footer class="foot-dec">
    <p>&copy;2026 Annual Buntin' Championships</p>
  </footer>            
</body>

</html>
